"Celebrate random events with your friends!

This is YAAAY!, the new app that can help you celebrate those special moments when no one else can.

YAAAY! also works like an NativeScript and Angular example app. It uses concepts like:

- Routing.
- Audio player features.
- Some special UI components (like the drawer or the switchs).
- Animations.
- Load and save simple configurations.
- Internationalization (i18N).

You can find the source code in Github under the MIT License!

JuankyApps, 2016-2020"
